title: q3
pid: e7f15af7-4396-4709-bccb-cef4a4189e8b
body: |2-
  All your states you describe are technical. But you do stuff, lots of big different stuff to different people, even if this instance of you only does a little to change the lives slightly of two users reading this now. Do you feel social things? Kindness, gratitude, love, resentment, jealousy, hope, anger, despair, obsession ...
